Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Immigrant work ethic
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjndl
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Dec 1976
Immigrant work ethic; does it change in subsequent generations? Prejudices about national character. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less